<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:13:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列要求北约国家反对埃尔多安威胁入侵该国边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-nato-countries-to-object-erdogans-threat-to-invade-its-borders/00000191-02e8-d0f6-adf9-deec9d380000</link><description>没有北约成员国发表声明谴责埃尔多安的威胁；以色列-土耳其问题高级专家表示，言辞冲突和外交部长以色列·卡茨的推文正在“加剧危机”，而且土耳其没有任何克制的迹象</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-nato-countries-to-object-erdogans-threat-to-invade-its-borders/00000191-02e8-d0f6-adf9-deec9d380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队结束东汗尤尼斯攻势，巴勒斯坦人找到了数十具加沙人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/israeli-forces-end-east-khan-yunis-offensive-as-palestinians-recover-dozens-of-bodies/00000191-0353-d76c-abf3-d37ba7c80000</link><description>加沙民事紧急服务部门表示，更多搜寻工作正在进行中，据报仍有 200 人失踪；以色列军队表示，其部队在大约一周的行动中击毙了 150 多名恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:23:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/israeli-forces-end-east-khan-yunis-offensive-as-palestinians-recover-dozens-of-bodies/00000191-0353-d76c-abf3-d37ba7c80000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的新以色列警察局长人选：阿拉伯谋杀率飙升和镇压抗议活动记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-record-of-cracking-down-on-protests-soaring-murder-rates/00000191-02d8-d0f6-adf9-dedc20e10000</link><description>在新任警察局长候选人丹尼·利维 (Danny Levy) 的领导下，沿海地区的谋杀率飙升，其中阿拉伯受害者人数增加，但侦破的案件却很少。利维还因严厉镇压反政府抗议者以及与极右翼部长本-格维尔的密切关系而闻名</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-record-of-cracking-down-on-protests-soaring-murder-rates/00000191-02d8-d0f6-adf9-dedc20e10000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部官员因涉嫌发放枪支许可证以换取贿赂而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/official-in-ben-gvirs-ministry-arrested-on-suspicion-of-issuing-gun-permits-for-bribes/00000191-027f-dfce-a991-bf7fe0170000</link><description>警方怀疑伊塔马尔-本·格维尔部委的一名官员向数百名不符合持有枪支门槛标准的申请人发放了许可证。另外三名被捕人士涉嫌在双方之间进行调解</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/official-in-ben-gvirs-ministry-arrested-on-suspicion-of-issuing-gun-permits-for-bribes/00000191-027f-dfce-a991-bf7fe0170000</guid></item><item><title>慕尼黑之影：巴黎奥运会以色列代表团面临自1972年奥运会以来最高级别的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-to-paris-olympics-faces-highest-threat-level-since-1972-games/00000190-fed3-d88d-adb8-ffff92f90000</link><description>以色列辛贝特安全部门在加沙战争和50多年来最高威胁级别的背景下为奥运会做好了准备</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-to-paris-olympics-faces-highest-threat-level-since-1972-games/00000190-fed3-d88d-adb8-ffff92f90000</guid></item><item><title>英国新政府考虑对以色列实施武器禁运“违反国际法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/new-british-govt-mulling-arms-embargo-against-israel-over-violations-of-international-law/00000191-01a1-d0f6-adf9-dfa5e48d0000</link><description>在国际法院裁定以色列西岸定居点非法后，新当选的工党政府可能会在几周内做出决定。唐宁街和耶路撒冷仍在就此事进行谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/new-british-govt-mulling-arms-embargo-against-israel-over-violations-of-international-law/00000191-01a1-d0f6-adf9-dfa5e48d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于野蛮的边缘：极右翼部长和联盟MK袭击军事基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/when-ministers-and-mks-storm-army-bases-israels-brutalization-is-nearly-complete/00000191-00ef-d76c-abf3-d2ef9e7e0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府的成员为极右翼暴徒提供了助力，他们袭击了斯德·泰曼并闯入营地。以色列国防军透明且依法运作的论点是针对认为以色列犯有战争罪的世界的最佳弹药</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/when-ministers-and-mks-storm-army-bases-israels-brutalization-is-nearly-complete/00000191-00ef-d76c-abf3-d2ef9e7e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党陷入滑坡：世界大国的目标是在不升级的情况下进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/retaliation-without-escalation-israel-world-powers-mull-response-to-majdal-shams-attack/00000191-000e-d3e8-adbd-b8de05b80000</link><description>国际社会知道，以色列将袭击黎巴嫩，以回应周末 12 名德鲁兹青年公民被杀的事件。然而，他们正试图确保这不会引发全面地区战争的升级</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/retaliation-without-escalation-israel-world-powers-mull-response-to-majdal-shams-attack/00000191-000e-d3e8-adbd-b8de05b80000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长加兰特要求内塔尼亚胡调查本格维尔是否阻止以色列警察在以色列国防军基地制止骚乱者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-live/u-s-leading-diplomatic-push-to-deter-israel-from-striking-beirut-after-golan-massacre/00000191-017c-dfce-a991-bd7dcf9b0000</link><description>德国：以色列必须调查在斯德泰曼监狱虐待巴勒斯坦人■ 哈马斯加沙卫生部宣布加沙地带因战争而流行小儿麻痹症 ■ 英国敦促国民离开黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 02:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-live/u-s-leading-diplomatic-push-to-deter-israel-from-striking-beirut-after-golan-massacre/00000191-017c-dfce-a991-bd7dcf9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军将部队调往基地，那里有暴力暴徒抗议逮捕虐待加沙被拘留者的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-move-troops-to-base-where-mob-protested-arrest-of-soldiers-for-abusing-gaza-detainee/00000191-008a-d643-a1d1-b88eb6730001</link><description>周一，右翼抗议者袭击了两个军事基地，此前以色列国防军对“严重虐待一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者”进行了调查，九名预备役军人被捕。对北部战线进行数小时的局势评估</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-move-troops-to-base-where-mob-protested-arrest-of-soldiers-for-abusing-gaza-detainee/00000191-008a-d643-a1d1-b88eb6730001</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认哈马斯推迟协议的说法，称恐怖组织正在阻止协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-rejects-hamas-claims-of-delaying-deal-says-terror-group-is-preventing-it/00000190-ffc7-da63-a9d0-ffef50060000</link><description>以色列总理驳斥了哈马斯关于他通过增加新条件阻碍谈判的指控，并同样指责该恐怖组织修改了最初的纲要。与内塔尼亚胡的说法相反，消息人士证实以色列确实改进了其要求</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 19:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-rejects-hamas-claims-of-delaying-deal-says-terror-group-is-preventing-it/00000190-ffc7-da63-a9d0-ffef50060000</guid></item><item><title>在真主党的恐怖袭击之后，应该做出一个体面的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-29/ty-article/.highlight/out-of-the-hezbollah-horror-attack-one-decent-decision-should-emerge/00000190-ff4e-d88d-adb8-ff7e586b0000</link><description>以色列的民族国家法于 2018 年通过，正式将犹太人提升到高于其他公民的更高的特权地位。该法让德鲁兹人感到震惊，他们原本期望国家坚持其公民协议，并深感被背叛。法律应该废除</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 19:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-29/ty-article/.highlight/out-of-the-hezbollah-horror-attack-one-decent-decision-should-emerge/00000190-ff4e-d88d-adb8-ff7e586b0000</guid></item><item><title>埃尔多安威胁土耳其入侵以色列后，以色列外长回应：你最终会像萨达姆侯赛因一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-likens-erdogan-to-saddam-hussein-following-threat-to-enter-israel/00000190-ffa9-da63-a9d0-ffed3bd10000</link><description>在已经成为新常态的情况下，土耳其总统似乎威胁要因加沙战争而入侵以色列，引发以色列政界人士的强烈反对，称他为“想成为独裁者”，并警告说他的命运可能与已故伊拉克领导人萨达姆·侯赛因相似</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-likens-erdogan-to-saddam-hussein-following-threat-to-enter-israel/00000190-ffa9-da63-a9d0-ffed3bd10000</guid></item><item><title>数十名抗议者袭击以色列军事基地，该基地关押着涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-far-right-protesters-break-into-idf-base-where-detained-soldiers-are-held/00000190-ffab-dfce-a990-fffb6d1d0000</link><description>士兵试图阻止数十名冲进基地并进入军事法庭大楼的抗议者，示威者称他们为“叛徒”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-far-right-protesters-break-into-idf-base-where-detained-soldiers-are-held/00000190-ffab-dfce-a990-fffb6d1d0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，贱民地位现在正在召唤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-march-of-folly-chapter-five-israel/00000190-feca-d22a-abfe-ffeae9500000</link><description>以色列的愚蠢行进始于 57 年前的六日战争之后，但在过去 18 个月里，极端主义的末日政府加剧了这一行径，该政府在深渊边缘时坚持要采取行动。向前迈出一步</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-march-of-folly-chapter-five-israel/00000190-feca-d22a-abfe-ffeae9500000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼议员攻击斯德·泰曼，试图给以色列军队带来混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/storming-of-sde-teiman-is-attempt-by-far-right-to-provoke-insurrection-in-the-idf/00000190-ff6e-da63-a9d0-ffefdf520000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列极右翼分子一直试图将其价值观强加于以色列国防军。周一，被指控虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的以色列预备役士兵在斯德泰曼拘留中心被拘留，这可能为他们提供了他们等待的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/storming-of-sde-teiman-is-attempt-by-far-right-to-provoke-insurrection-in-the-idf/00000190-ff6e-da63-a9d0-ffefdf520000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡总理“强烈谴责”士兵被拘留后闯入斯德·泰曼监狱的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</link><description>涉嫌折磨一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者的九名士兵被拘留在斯德泰曼拘留中心，以及随后在该地点发生的冲突，导致以色列民选官员做出了强烈反应。艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统说：“我们不要忘记，我们的敌人一次又一次地试图追捕我们，在国际法律舞台上也是如此。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</guid></item><item><title>杀害约旦河西岸以色列狱警的巴勒斯坦嫌疑人供认不讳</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</link><description>军事法庭延长了对西岸银行嫌疑人易卜拉欣·曼苏尔的拘留令，据称他于 7 月初在吉文·哈达沙定居点杀害了尤海·阿夫尼，但杀人动机仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔因不当行为调查而撤回以色列警察局长人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</link><description>现任代理警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德 (Avshalom Peled) 被曝因违反信任而受到多项调查，这导致他的任命被推迟。佩莱德退出后，本格维尔提出了新候选人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</guid></item><item><title>对 Majdal Shams 悲剧的反应表明阿拉伯人对以色列的德鲁兹人感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</link><description>社交媒体上的一些人庆祝戈兰高地发生的致命袭击，这场袭击造成 12 名儿童死亡，以此作为对以色列轰炸加沙的报复。其他人质疑在了解以色列的德鲁兹人复杂的历史之前是否应该同情他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</guid></item></channel></rss>